# 파이썬 자료구조 시각화

## 환경설정

파이썬 자료구조 시각화를 위해 [lolviz](https://github.com/parrt/lolviz) 패키지를 설치한다.

::: {.cell execution_count=1}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# !pip3 install lolviz
```
:::


## 헬로월드

[lolviz](https://github.com/parrt/lolviz) 패키지 README.md 파일에 기술된 코드를 넣어 제대로 헬로월드를 찍어보자

::: {.cell execution_count=2}
``` {.python .cell-code}
from lolviz import *
data = ['hi','mom',{3,4},{"parrt":"user"}]
g = listviz(data)
g
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=2}
![](python_data_structure_files/figure-html/cell-3-output-1.svg){}
:::
:::


# 자료구조 시각화

## list of lists

::: {.cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

# list of lists 생성
list_of_lists = [['Alex', 10], ['Bob', 12], ['Clarke', 13]]

listviz(list_of_lists)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=3}
![](python_data_structure_files/figure-html/cell-4-output-1.svg){}
:::
:::


::: {.cell execution_count=4}
``` {.python .cell-code}
lolviz(list_of_lists)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=4}
![](python_data_structure_files/figure-html/cell-5-output-1.svg){}
:::
:::


